title: HOUR 1 - Cowboys & Brand Loyalty

description:
Doug Gottlieb, in for Colin Cowherd, talks about the Cowboys and brand loyalty, LA Times Lakers reporter Dan Woike joins the show to talk about the Lakers options, and the 49ers justify keeping Jimmy G around.
